e\": \"\\\"It has not been in that happy zone sincethe last time we hosted the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that happy zone sincethe\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, the state's inland sea and capital city namesake islimping by on 2023's record-setting winter.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Today, the state's inland sea and capital city namesake islimping\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"2023's record-setting winter\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Otherwise, the challenges that have threatened to dry the lake upin five yearsstill remain - the West's ongoing drought, agricultural diversions and burgeoning urbanand industrial growtharound Salt Lake City.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 676, \"end\": 690, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999960859896, \"rank\": 3.6409520364775327e-09, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the challenges\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"the lake upin\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"the West's ongoing drought\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"agricultural diversions\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are not anywhere at that sustainable elevation, and we would need to bring the lake up about 5.5 feet in the south and about 8 feet in the north to get it back to that happy zone.\\\"\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that sustainable elevation\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"the lake\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"about 5.5 feet\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"the south\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"about 8 feet\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"the north\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"that happy zone\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Utah's standing asthe likely hostof the 2034 Winter Games, more international attention could land on the challenges the lake faces likesalinity and brine shrimpor the exposed lakebed.\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2735202329884474e-12, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"asthe likely hostof\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2034 Winter Games\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"more international attention\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 971}, {\"ngram\": \"the challenges\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"the lake\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"likesalinity\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"shrimpor\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"the exposed lakebed\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know, the optics are not going to be good if the Olympics are getting blasted with a lakebed dust storm,\\\" Larsen noted.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the optics\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"a lakebed dust storm\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1178}, {\"ngram\": \"Larsen\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A big problem with the lake bed dust is that itfalls on the snowand makes it melt faster.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \