\"thatBrian\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"10 years\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next Olympics is a possibility but it would take a lot of conservation to get there.\\\"\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The next Olympics\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"a possibility\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1859}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"conservation\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This interview has been edited for length and clarity Pamela McCall: What would have to happen for the lake elevation to become sustainable in 10 years?\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pamela_Rebecca_Barnes\", \"score\": 0.9999975664047778, \"rank\": 2.4335954266789393e-06, \"text\": \"Pamela\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pamela_Rebecca_Barnes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pamela_Rebecca_Barnes\"}, {\"begin\": 1978, \"end\": 1984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_McCall\", \"score\": 0.9999998369603551, \"rank\": 1.630371576213597e-07, \"text\": \"McCall\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_McCall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_McCall\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This interview\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1930}, {\"ngram\": \"length\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"clarity\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"the lake elevation\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"10 years\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leia Larsen:The strategic plan is that we are going to need to do about 1.3 million acre-feet of additional conservation each year in times of drought - and about 700,000 acre-feet of water a year in a normal period where we get normal snowpack and normal runoff.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2334, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The strategic plan\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"about 1.3 million acre-feet\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"additional conservation\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2210}, {\"ngram\": \"drought\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2260}, {\"ngram\": \"a normal period\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"normal snowpack\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"normal runoff\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know it's hard to wrap your mind around what an acre-foot is, but, to put that in context a little bit, 1.3 million acre-feet is water that all agriculture in the Great Salt Lake Basin uses each year in times of drought.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your mind\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2369}, {\"ngram\": \"an acre-foot\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"1.3 million acre-feet\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2462}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2471}, {\"ngram\": \"all agriculture\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2492}, {\"ngram\": \"the Great Salt Lake Basin\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"drought\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is the amount of water we would need to conserve each year to get the Great Salt Lake back to its minimum healthy elevation.\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2576}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"the Great Salt Lake\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2648}, {\"ngram\": \"its minimum healthy elevation\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PM: How would that be achieved?\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2720, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LL:Lawmakers in the last few years have passed a number of reforms to our water law.\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lawmakers\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2734}, {\"ngram\": \"the last few years\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"reforms\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"our water law\", \"from\": 2792, \"to\": 2805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have spent a lot of money on conservation, investing more than$250 million in both secondary meteringfor cities and municipalities.\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2943, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2828}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"conservation\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2853}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2923}, {\"ngram\": \"municipalities\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's so people will know how much water they are using outdoors.\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"how much water\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About the same amount of money's been spent on agriculture water optimization.\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"About the same amount\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3041}, {\"ngram\": \"agriculture water optimization\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those are two big programs that are likely to conserve a lot of water.\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two big programs\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3116}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The problem is, right now we do not know how much is being saved and where it's all going.\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The problem\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do not know if it's reaching the lake.\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lake\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I think a big thing that you will see lawmakers may be focusing on this session is equipment just to measure the water.\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big thing\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"lawmakers\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3344}, {\"ngram\": \"this session\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"equipment\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where is it in real time and how is it going to the lake?\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"real time\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"the lake\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That will be a big part of the strategy.\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big part\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"the strategy\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am also curious where we had such a good snowpack last year - and we are having an average snowpack so far this year - whether that maybe will slow the discussion about the Great Salt Lake in the Legislature.\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a good snowpack\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"an average snowpack\", \"from\": 3599, \"to\": 3618}, {\"ngram\": \"the discussion\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3681}, {\"ngram\": \"the Great Salt Lake\", \"from\": 3688, \"to\": 3707}, {\"ngram\": \"the Legislature\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think maybe there is a bit of Great Salt Lake fatigue going around, even among Utahns.\", \"from\": 3728, \"to\": 3816, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"Great Salt Lake fatigue\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3783}, {\"ngram\": \"Utahns\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a hard issue to confront over the last couple of years and it seems so difficult to solve.\", \"from\": 3817, \"to\": 3917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hard issue\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3839}, {\"ngram\": \"the last couple\", \"from\": 3857, \"to\": 3872}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 3881}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PM: How realistic is it that the Great Salt Lake will be healthy again in 10 years?\", \"from\": 3919, \"to\": 4002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Great Salt Lake\", \"from\": 3948, \"to\": 3967}, {\"ngram\": \"10 years\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LL:Part of it is going to depend on the weather and what kind of snow we get in the next ten years.\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Part\", \"from\": 4007, \"to\": 4011}, {\"ngram\": \"the weather\", \"from\": 4040, \"to\": 4051}, {\"ngram\": \"what kind\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4065}, {\"ngram\": \"snow\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4073}, {\"ngram\": \"the next ten years\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And a big part of it's going to have to do with just how committed Utahns are to getting water to the lake and participating in these programs and doing their part.\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big part\", \"from\": 4108, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"Utahns\", \"from\": 4171, \"to\": 4177}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4198}, {\"ngram\": \"the lake\", \"from\": 4202, \"to\": 4210}, {\"ngram\": \"these programs\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4246}, {\"ngram\": \"their part\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 4267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's really kind of - that fate is in our hands.\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that fate\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4303}, {\"ngram\": \"our hands\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4319}]}]}"